data.value:
This program solution for efficient bookstore management. Our software simplifies inventory organization, sales tracking, and customer management, ensuring smooth operations for any bookstore, big or small. With intuitive features and insightful reporting, this program empowers booksellers to streamline their processes and enhance customer satisfaction.
This program was made by Annie Ronne L. Azul from Bicol University BSIT-3B (2023- 2024) to comply with IT120's requirements.
